      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah that makes sense. we're specifically using a sateen weave for this line to get that smooth finish. since we're aiming for that ultra-high density to ensure the fabric is really tightly sealed and stays intact, do you think there's a limit to how much we should tighten the weave before we start compromising the integrity of the fibers?",
